  "instructions": [
    "In a medium saucepan, heat the ghee over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped small onion and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the porcini mushrooms and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the cooked white rice, salt, and smoked paprika. Stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a large serving dish.",
    "Using a whisk, mix in the fermented cream until the pilaf is smooth and creamy.",
    "Add the chopped parsley, scallions, and dill. Mix until combined.",
    "Top with the burrata ball and drizzle with lemon juice and olive oil. Serve immediately."
